		background-size: contain;
	}
	.ongiri {
		background-color: black;
		height: 40px;
		width: 40px;
		display: inline-block;
		background-image: url('ongiri.png');
		background-size: contain;
	}
	.blank {
		background-color:blue;
		height: 40px;
		width: 40px;
		display: inline-block;
	}
	#ninjaman {
		background-color: black;
		height: 40px;
